{"tid":1616531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搞Starbuck=自取滅亡","createTime":"2019-10-03T12:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T15:23:10.000Z","uid":292925,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6549329043a4ecc74cb7436af3da9d31e27cd69f","tid":1616531,"uid":292925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">搞Starbuck=自取滅亡</span></span><br />\n香港求緊美國幫手但係自己去打爆人地D野, 想點?冇撚病啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外國人唔會理亦都唔會花時間了解Starbucks同美心關係</span><br />\n佢地只係見到平時最鍾重飲既Starbuck比Crazy Hong Kong people打爆哂<br />\nStarbuck Coffee對鬼佬黎講等於香港魚蛋燒買, 你地想像下香港小食檔比外國人打爆哂你有咩感受?<br />\n香港人一直都係做緊「被害者」呢個角色先會比國際同情,支持<br />\n宜家人地會覺得香港人變左「施暴者」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人開始殺鬼佬啦!好恐怖呀!</span><br />\n<br />\n認真想問點解呢D全部冇事:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中資Pacific Coffee<br />\n中資華潤超市<br />\n奶共張敬軒 空中酒吧 The Crown<br />\n奶共余文樂 華嫂冰室 </span><br />\n <br />\n咁多野唔搞係都要搞9美國野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f724c25ce504a458e1a4782157da61d766569237","tid":1616531,"uid":292925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8d5ded4dc9af4271b089810903cf24ee3ee9a1","tid":1616531,"uid":292925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449e9eebee5155a0e13638bceb4d01261d948c1a","tid":1616531,"uid":85574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"老話咗唔係紅色企業/藍色政見就打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞美心、優品、富臨係有原因㗎大佬"},{"pid"